After a long time, the master of these servants returned. He wanted to gather all the money they had earned.
The man who received $10,000 brought the other $10,000. He said, "Sir, you trusted me with $10,000. Look, I've made another $10,000."
His master answered him, "Well done, good and faithful servant! You have been faithful over a little; I will set you over much. Enter into the joy of your master!"
The man with $4000 also came. He said, "Sir, you trusted me with $4000. Look, I've made another $4000."
